{"tid":2278033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普不只輸了選戰 英媒爆第一夫人正在協商離婚","createTime":"2020-11-09T01:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T06:09:59.000Z","uid":290118,"like":25,"dislike":224,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"b11d67009f3e256555c606738d9db01700c39ea0","tid":2278033,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:35:26.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普輸了選舉，現在媒體又報導，第一夫人梅蘭妮亞（Melania Trump）要離婚。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》報導，梅蘭妮亞在2016年川普當選總統時後大哭。她的好友透露，梅蘭妮亞完全沒想到川普會當選總統。<br />\n<br />\n川普當選後，梅蘭妮亞拖了5個月才從紐約搬去華盛頓，據稱是要等小兒子拜倫（Barron Trump）小學畢業。<br />\n<br />\n梅蘭妮亞前閨蜜吳可芙（Stephanie Winston Wolkoff）稱，梅蘭妮亞正在協商一份離婚協議，以便讓自己與川普的兒子拜倫能拿到約定的財產及遺產。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201109/LQOORERC55HQLICXOYXMXLH7FI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201109%2FLQOORERC55HQLICXOYXMXLH7FI%2F&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BaGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=5e38437a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201109%2FLQOORERC55HQLICXOYXMXLH7FI%2F&h=8bc0125d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201109/LQOORERC55HQLICXOYXMXLH7FI/</a>"},{"pid":"8bf3eb530f449adb4ca5c3e72d40a1f9709c04ab","tid":2278033,"uid":241171,"like":178,"dislike":12,"score":166,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2BB2fGM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2BB2fGM.jpg&h=ba1b0656&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41cdb40367dccfb5b66ce7c5e4403a83f15215d8","tid":2278033,"uid":211110,"like":15,"dislike":116,"score":-101,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:37:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b93c14ab48dde09b023f15561726c0aaba41506","tid":2278033,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8bf3eb530f449adb4ca5c3e72d40a1f9709c04ab","tid":2278033,"uid":241171,"like":178,"dislike":12,"score":166,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-0