0,"quote":{"pid":"ceff3878af41b0bd89d18002cf5203e8cd858a79","tid":2278033,"uid":253119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e8b407607c8dd9ae5186c5ae4c9f493e808f390","tid":2278033,"uid":223198,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"860fb78015304c9b4d92b85744983750f430b901","tid":2278033,"uid":210669,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:44:33.000Z","msg":"好似已經傳左好多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:58:26.000Z","msg":"由上任果時已經話離, 離咗4年都未得, 但d 垃圾報紙次次都報 <br />\n通俄又係報足幾年<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老味成班左媒雙重標準"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51J8b17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51J8b17.jpg&h=8b8905db&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:05:28.000Z","msg":"希拉莉和民主黨大會(DNC)出錢聘用這家公司去發掘特朗普醜聞，為了掩人耳目，希拉莉和民主黨大會將錢交給一家名為Perkins Coie律師行，再由律師行將錢交給Fusion GPS​。<br />\n<br />\nFusion GPS和這份Dossier有什麼關係?<br />\n<br />\nFusion GPS聘用了Nelli Ohr負責這件工作，部分資料(許多是來自俄國人)由Christoper Steele提供，其餘由Nelli Ohr起草內容。毫無疑問​，這份文件是希拉莉和民主黨聯同奧巴馬政府司法部​/FBI​​共同炮製對付競選對手特朗普的秘密武器​​。<br />\n<br />\n希拉莉和民主黨如何使用Dossier去打擊對手?<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬政府司法部和​FBI四次使用這份Dossier的虛假資料，成功地向​​法庭取得竊聽令，在競選期間非法向特朗普團隊進行竊聽。此外，希拉莉在競選過程當中(包括與特朗普三場辯論)不斷公開指責特朗普私通蘇俄。他們明明知道這些是假資料，照樣用來打擊對手，並且不斷向傳媒洩漏假消息，讓民眾長期(包括特朗普當選之後)以為​特朗普有通俄之嫌​，因此他競選勝利是違法的​​​。 另一方面，這份Dossier也間接帶來特別調查員對特朗普進行兩年多的調查，其目的是要將特朗普拉下台。"},{"pid":"b0e2f97d55304098d8e739edf0dea5939f07009a","tid":2278033,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c63d4478e2d0893adaaa51b773440ec3bf4fb765","tid":2278033,"uid":16057,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:42:38.000Z","msg":"侵唔係日日都講緊離婚 屋企家嘈屋閉 冇人撐佢咩 <br />\n<br />\n外國主流傳媒話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:08:42.000Z","msg":"由佢做生意個陣都傳緊啦<br />\n傳到之後出埋個SHOW有埋金句&quot;YOU'RE  FIRED!&quot;<br />\n有埋金句都傳緊傳到佢四年前上任前都仲傳緊<br />\n傳到今年大選前都仲傳緊<br />\n再傳到佢個仔個女都係自己個twitter開聲都仲傳緊<br />\n睇怕呢個新聞應該傳到佢入棺材佢老婆死埋<br />\n都應該仲傳緊佢老婆打算離婚<br />\n<br />\n佢老婆年紀都唔細加上侵已經換左唔少次老婆食過唔少女<br />\n我諗白痴都知佢性格如果要離婚應該要搵個最值錢既時候離先有用"},{"pid":"80742370303d5210f303dd6468537de0fad48c76","tid":2278033,"uid":222392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:11:01.000Z","msg":"CNN = 美國版環球時報！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9776ffd845cda516707fab010fe5de0269f9916d","tid":2278033,"uid":379666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e57eb640c0757897ab797a7ffa5f1d6ffdbf3b5e","tid":2278033,"uid":290118,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"35ffe9acdadd888ad9af19f26e7f7b5a1d0ad811","tid":2278033,"uid":343643,"like":94,"dislike":1,"score":93,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:46:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/flotus/status/1325509832594616328?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fflotus%2Fstatus%2F1325509832594616328%3Fs%3D21&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BaGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=767d3495\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fflotus%2Fstatus%2F1325509832594616328%3Fs%3D21&h=ee42e20f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/flotus/status/1325509832594616328?s=21</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:53:30.000Z","msg":"已伸請删post, 勿推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:12:30.000Z","msg":"假新聞 虛假消息 已report<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"974037110c2b652ac7dbc063e3a64f2bc6999467","tid":2278033,"uid":313974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"41cdb40367dccfb5b66ce7c5e4403a83f15215d8","tid":2278033,"uid":211110,"like":15,"dislike":116,"score":-101,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:37:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:22:43.000Z","msg":"你就Loser<br />\n淨係識嘴砲"}]}